OL,3,CAdult fostering scheme trying to
OL,4,Ctackle lack of carers in South West
OL,6,FShared Lives South West is appealing
OL,7,Ffor carers who can open up their own
OL,8,Fhome to someone in need.
OL,10,FShared Lives has been compared to
OL,11,Ffostering for adults.
OL,13,FCarer Melanie Thomas has hosted Abby
OL,14,FGaylard and her daughter Isabella for
OL,15,Fthe last five years in her Camborne
OL,16,Fhome.
OL,18,FAfter working in the care sector and
OL,19,Fraising her own children, Melanie
OL,20,Fdecided she wanted to take on a role
OL,21,Fwhere she could help another mum.
