OL,6,FShe said: ''Many years ago I wanted to
OL,7,Ffoster but after working with parents
OL,8,Fand children, you can make life better
OL,9,Ffor a child but to make it good for
OL,10,Fthe long term, you have to work with a
OL,11,Fparent and a child to make it
OL,12,Fsustainable for that child.
OL,14,F"It's been amazing watching them grow
OL,15,Fand to try new challenges and seeing
OL,16,Fthem face new things. Isabella hitting
OL,17,Fall of her milestones, learning to
OL,18,Fswim. Abby, setting goals for herself,
OL,19,Fjust watching her thrive and become a
OL,20,Fmore confident person and a parent."
