OL,6,FYoung mum Abby was looking for a
OL,7,Fstable home setting that could help
OL,8,Fsupport her with parenting Isabella.
OL,9,FFor them moving into a shared lives
OL,10,Fhome was the right fit.
OL,12,FAbby said: "I've changed as a person.
OL,13,FI've become a great mum to Isabella
OL,14,Fnow and her family's really supported
OL,15,Fme. And I wouldn't know where I'd be
OL,16,Fwithout them now, today.
