OL,6,F"It was very hard when I lived at
OL,7,Fhome, and I'm glad we're here because
OL,8,Fnow we've come very far. They love us
OL,9,Fand look after us really well, support
OL,10,Fus. It's really lovely."
OL,12,FEdward Bunce-Phillips works for Shared
OL,13,FLives South West. His own parents were
OL,14,FShared Lives carers - and as the
OL,15,Fcharity marks its 20th anniversary
OL,16,Fit's looking for more carers to open
OL,17,Fup their homes.
