OL,3,CAdult fostering scheme trying to
OL,4,Ctackle lack of carers in South West
OL,6,FEdward said: ''Some people use the
OL,7,Fservice just to have short breaks. So
OL,8,Fthe principal carers might be their
OL,9,Ffamily, but to give the families
OL,10,Frespite, so they might just stay with
OL,11,Fa carer occasionally, and then lots of
OL,12,Fpeople who, you know, make a home for
OL,13,Flife or as a stepping stone so for a
OL,14,Fyear, two years where they build up
OL,15,Fsome skills and in order to go and
OL,16,Flive a more independent life
OL,17,Felsewhere. So it really varies."
OL,19,FCornwall Council says there is a
OL,20,Fcritical need for more carers like
OL,21,FMelanie.
