OL,3,CAdult fostering scheme trying to
OL,4,Ctackle lack of carers in South West
OL,6,F"And it's a great alternative to maybe
OL,7,Fhaving to put someone into residential
OL,8,Fcare. So it can keep people actually
OL,9,Fliving in the community and it's much
OL,10,Fbetter for people."
OL,12,FFor anyone considering signing up it's
OL,13,Fhelpful to have some care experience
OL,14,Fbut the role comes with training.
